responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "8FB8D6BA4D505622BAFFA2964C699993", "Come and dance four sisters of Sephillion. Dance the dance and wish for me. Lyndra oh most beautiful. What wonders do you wish to see? Let my beauty go unmatched. A radiant bloom from hill to sea. Let all grow of fondness and allure. The paragon of beauty, me.")
